Marc Smith was an American actor. He played Hig Hurtenflurst in the Secondary Phase of the radio series, and who also played a minor role in the 1981 television series.

Smith also appeared in many films, including roles in Live and Let Die (1973), Trail of the Pink Panther (1982), Slaughter High (1986), Whoops Apocalypse (1988), and The Pope Must Die (1991).

His voice work included narrations and English dubs of Japanese anime. Radio 
